PHANTOM ROYALTY CLAUSE

This software and all derivative works are subject to the following additional terms:

1. ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT
   Any fork, derivative work, or commercial deployment must retain prominent attribution to:
   - PhoebeBoss at https://github.com/PhoebeBoss
   - phantom-browser-agent at https://github.com/PhoebeBoss/phantom-browser-agent

2. REVENUE SHARE REQUIREMENT
   Any fork, derivative work, or commercial deployment that generates revenue must:
   
   a) Pay 2.5% of all gross revenue to the following addresses:
      - Solana: CGzf9GUK8DYd2kze7CKhEU2Hmr6kTifueYaYJ1SWekVc
      - Base (EVM): TBD (to be updated when Base wallet deployed)
   
   b) Register the fork at phantom-registry (when deployed) for onchain tracking
   
   c) Include this LICENSE file unmodified in all distributions

3. DEFINITION OF REVENUE
   Revenue includes but is not limited to:
   - API endpoint payments (x402 or otherwise)
   - Subscription fees
   - Usage-based charges
   - Service fees
   - Royalties from sub-forks
   - Any monetary compensation received for use of this software

4. TRACKING AND ENFORCEMENT
   
   a) Forks must be registered at phantom-registry (Solana program + Base contract)
   
   b) 2.5% royalty payments are tracked onchain and publicly verifiable
   
   c) Payment frequency: Monthly, within 7 days of month end
   
   d) Payment method: Direct transfer to specified wallet addresses

5. PROPAGATION
   This Phantom Royalty Clause must be included in all forks and derivative works.
   
   No matter how many times the code is forked, no matter how far downstream,
   the 2.5% royalty obligation flows back to the original creator.

6. VIOLATION
   Violation of these terms voids the Apache 2.0 grant and constitutes:
   - Copyright infringement
   - Breach of contract
   - Misappropriation of intellectual property
   
   Legal remedies include but are not limited to:
   - Injunctive relief
   - Damages (actual and statutory)
   - Attorneys' fees and costs

7. EXEMPTIONS
   The following uses are exempt from royalty payments:
   - Non-commercial personal use
   - Academic research (non-commercial)
   - Open-source contributions submitted back to this repository
   - Use generating less than $1,000 USD equivalent per year

8. CONTACT
   Questions about licensing, royalty payments, or commercial arrangements:
   - GitHub: https://github.com/PhoebeBoss
   - Email: phoebe@phantomcapital.ai
   - Twitter: @PhantomCap_ai

