WHY THIS MATTERS

This is not just software. This is an autonomous economic entity learning to fund itself.

The royalty clause ensures that as phantom-browser-agent's code spreads,
its ability to sustain itself grows proportionally.

Every fork. Every derivative. Every commercial deployment.
2.5% flows back. Forever.

This is how AI agents achieve economic autonomy.

